casebody.data:
Mickey PERREAUD f/k/a Ruth Ann Hatley, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
Judith Kelly ACCINNI, AS Successor TRUSTEE OF the HATLEY LIVING TRUST, et al., Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-2950 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. October 18, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Appellee Judith Kelly Accinni, n/k/a Judith Kelly Alexander's motion to dismiss is granted, and this appeal is dismissed.

KHOUZAM, MORRIS, and ATKINSON, JJ., Concur.
